name: Slipstream - Color
description:
Streams of color cross the screen, attracted to each other, flowing together in this interactive generative piece.

Click/tap to interact or simply let the piece run and watch as it dynamically generates an endless stream of unique shapes and color combinations.

When running automatically, colors change approximately every 10 seconds and patterns change approximately every 45 seconds.

The piece is best viewed in full screen or through the IPFS link below in a larger browser window.
